ng or original, but OK. I would spend your money at a steakhouse like Craftsteak rather than wasting it at a wannabe steakhouse like that. We have all kinds of snobby wannabe hipster places back home and there are running rampant in Vegas... spend the money and go for the real deal instead.One last thing..we did have a few really nice waitresses in the casino itself. The pretty blond mom of a 14 year old (was getting off of work to take her back to school shopping) who showed my friends how to figure out the 1cent slots was such a sweetie (worked Thursday and Friday night). I wish I remembered her name. Thanks anyway!	
